SUBSTITUTE FOR
HOUSE BILL NO. 4588
A bill to amend 1954 PA 116, entitled
"Michigan election law,"
by amending sections 303, 534, 697, and 699 (MCL 168.303, 168.534,
168.697, and 168.699), section 303 as amended by 2018 PA 650,
section 534 as amended by 2018 PA 224, section 697 as amended by
2018 PA 226, and section 699 as amended by 2012 PA 523.
THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF MICHIGAN ENACT:
